<h2 align="center"><!--mstheme--><font face="Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times"><span style="font-weight: 400"><font size="7" face="Verdana">
Historical summary </font></span><!--mstheme--></font></h2>
<p align="center"><font size="2">
